# Alert — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/alert.css`

## Architecture

ALL styling in CSS via `@apply` + raw CSS. React only composes class names via `clsx`. Inline SVGs for default icons (no lucide-react).

## CSS Classes

### Base
`.acko-alert` — `@apply flex gap-3 relative`, padding `--space-4`, border-radius `--radius-3xl`, border 1px solid

### Variants
| Class | Background | Border |
|-------|------------|--------|
| `.acko-alert-info` | `--color-info-subtle` | `--color-info-border` |
| `.acko-alert-success` | `--color-success-subtle` | `--color-success-border` |
| `.acko-alert-warning` | `--color-warning-subtle` | `--color-warning-border` |
| `.acko-alert-error` | `--color-error-subtle` | `--color-error-border` |

Icon and title use variant text color (e.g. `--color-info-text`).

### Children
- `.acko-alert-icon` — `--scale-20` size, color inherited from variant
- `.acko-alert-content` — flex-1, flex flex-col gap-1
- `.acko-alert-title` — `--font-body-sm-size`, font-weight 600
- `.acko-alert-body` — `--font-body-sm-size`, color `--color-text-default`
- `.acko-alert-dismiss` — absolute top/right `--space-3`, `--scale-24` size, opacity 0.7, hover opacity 1
